            <table border='0'>  <tr>    <td class='ind'><img src="s.gif" height="1" width="80"></td><td valign="top" class="votelinks"><center><a id='up_16527436' href='vote?id=16527436&amp;how=up&amp;goto=item%3Fid%3D16526461'><div class='votearrow' title='upvote'></div></a></center></td><td class="default"><div style="margin-top:2px; margin-bottom:-10px;"><span class="comhead">
          <a href="user?id=runeks" class="hnuser">runeks</a> <span class="age"><a href="item?id=16527436">3 hours ago</a></span> <span id="unv_16527436"></span><span class="par"></span> <a class="togg" n="2" href="javascript:void(0)" onclick="return toggle(event, 16527436)"></a>          <span class='storyon'></span>
                  </span></div><br><div class="comment">
                  <span class="c00">Humans also survive by ingesting other life forms (plants, animals). We couldn’t survive without vegetation either, because it converts our waste products into useful stuff (e.g. CO2 to oxygen).<span>
              </span><div class='reply'>        <p><font size="1">
