                  <span class="c00">By that definition you could say that pretty much anything that does something is a machine. A computer is an electrical machine, the Sun is a physical machine ... We choose to give specific names like &quot;computer&quot; or &quot;star&quot; or &quot;life&quot; to physical phenomenons which fit a particular definition. It&#x27;s mostly a way for us humans ot communicate and think about it. Life exists because we made up a word for it.<span>
              </span><div class='reply'>        <p><font size="1">
