                  </span></div><br><div class="comment">
                  <span class="c00">While I totally agree with you, there is some value in having a clear definition of life if you&#x27;re trying to do something like determine if it exists on other planets. In that sense, you&#x27;re looking for some kind of self-separating chemical unit, which looks very different from a homogenous soup which happens to undergo complex chemical reactions.<span>
